# db-query Development Guidelines

Auto-generated from feature plan 001-db-query-tool. Last updated: 2026-03-29

## Active Technologies

**Backend**: Python 3.12+ (uv), FastAPI, sqlglot, openai SDK, asyncpg, SQLite (stdlib sqlite3)
**Frontend**: TypeScript 5.x, React 18, Refine 5, Tailwind CSS, Ant Design 5, Monaco Editor
**Storage**: SQLite (~/.db_query/db_query.db), PostgreSQL (target, read-only)
**Platform**: Win10 + Docker Toolbox, docker-compose

