## Commands

```bash
# Start all services
docker-compose up --build

# Backend only (dev)
cd backend && uv run uvicorn app.main:app --reload

# Frontend only (dev)
cd frontend && npm run dev
```

## Code Style

**Backend**:
- Ergonomic Python: readable, idiomatic, avoid over-engineering
- All functions/methods MUST have full type annotations (PEP 604)
- All data models MUST use Pydantic v2 (inherit from AppBaseModel)
- All API responses MUST use camelCase (alias_generator=to_camel)
- CORS: allow_origins=["*"]
- No authentication middleware

**Frontend**:
- TypeScript only (.tsx/.ts), no .js files
- No `any` type without explicit comment justification
- All API response types MUST be defined in src/types/
- Use Refine 5 data hooks for data fetching

**SQL Safety**:
- All SQL MUST be validated with sqlglot (dialect="postgres")
- Only SELECT statements allowed
- Auto-append LIMIT 1000 if no LIMIT clause

